  "detailed_description": "Dis Pontibus 2 is a single-player puzzle game set in a procedurally-generated archipelago.<br><br>In this sequel to the first adventure, you are tasked with helping the archipelago's inhabitants by repairing their bridges, pushing and/or rotating their platforms.<br><br>But platforms are more fragile in this world! You can move them only a limited number of times.<br><br>Each game will be a different experience, with simple mechanics but very challenging gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/b777e1731290018db817f6a16197aa00.poster.avif?t=1655288448\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/b777e1731290018db817f6a16197aa00.webm?t=1655288448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/b777e1731290018db817f6a16197aa00.mp4?t=1655288448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/81b04c4833f0724c63ecb40679236e5e.poster.avif?t=1655288448\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/81b04c4833f0724c63ecb40679236e5e.webm?t=1655288448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/81b04c4833f0724c63ecb40679236e5e.mp4?t=1655288448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Dis Pontibus 2 is a single-player puzzle game set in a procedurally-generated archipelago.<br><br>In this sequel to the first adventure, you are tasked with helping the archipelago's inhabitants by repairing their bridges, pushing and/or rotating their platforms.<br><br>But platforms are more fragile in this world! You can move them only a limited number of times.<br><br>Each game will be a different experience, with simple mechanics but very challenging gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/b777e1731290018db817f6a16197aa00.poster.avif?t=1655288448\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/b777e1731290018db817f6a16197aa00.webm?t=1655288448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/b777e1731290018db817f6a16197aa00.mp4?t=1655288448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/81b04c4833f0724c63ecb40679236e5e.poster.avif?t=1655288448\" width=180 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/81b04c4833f0724c63ecb40679236e5e.webm?t=1655288448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2012020/extras/81b04c4833f0724c63ecb40679236e5e.mp4?t=1655288448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
